00:03:48.039 --> 00:03:48.639
Steward.

00:03:49.599 --> 00:03:50.520
Order Vice General Zhang.

00:03:52.400 --> 00:03:53.520
Enough, enough.

00:03:54.039 --> 00:03:55.599
Duke, Duke!

00:04:00.960 --> 00:04:02.879
Young Duke became a dog official!

00:04:07.080 --> 00:04:08.639
Nonsense, what dog official?

00:04:08.719 --> 00:04:09.479
Ling Gou Official.

00:04:10.759 --> 00:04:11.680
Yes, yes.

00:04:13.280 --> 00:04:13.840
Son,

00:04:14.240 --> 00:04:15.280
His Majesty let you

00:04:18.079 --> 00:04:20.000
Ling Gou Official is too minor a post.

00:04:20.560 --> 00:04:21.879
This is hard to handle.

00:04:24.319 --> 00:04:26.720
