00:04:27.120 --> 00:04:28.480
Now it's hard to back down.

00:04:29.800 --> 00:04:30.279
No.

00:04:30.920 --> 00:04:32.079
I'll go to the palace now.

00:04:32.600 --> 00:04:33.040
Father.

00:04:34.240 --> 00:04:35.480
If no one advocates negotiation,

00:04:35.720 --> 00:04:36.560
